n    Ruiyi Yan, Yugo Murawaki\n    https://arxiv.org/pdf/2508.20718v1\n2. 2512.09769v3 | 2025-12-10 | Defining Cost Function of Steganography with Large Language Models\n    Hanzhou Wu, Yige Wang\n    https://arxiv.org/pdf/2512.09769v3\n3. 2511.05319v2 | 2025-11-07 | $\\mathbf{S^2LM}$: Towards Semantic Steganography via Large Language Models\n    Huanqi Wu, Huangbiao Xu, Runfeng Xie, Jiaxin Cai\n    https://arxiv.org/pdf/2511.05319v2\n4. 2404.10229v2 | 2024-04-16 | Generative Text Steganography with Large Language Model\n    Jiaxuan Wu, Zhengxian Wu, Yiming Xue, Juan Wen\n    https://arxiv.org/pdf/2404.10229v2\n5. 2504.08977v1 | 2025-04-11 | Robust Steganography from Large Language Models\n    Neil Perry, Sanket Gupte, Nishant Pitta, Lior Rotem\n    https://arxiv.org/pdf/2504.08977v1\n\nQUERY: all:steganalysis AND all:text\n1. 1206.2914v1 | 2012-06-12 | Steganalysis Using Color Model Conversion\n    P. Thiyagarajan, G. Aghila, V. Prasanna Venkatesan\n    https://arxiv.org/pdf/1206.2914v1\n2. 1912.12871v2 | 2019-12-30 | Text Steganalysis with Attentional LSTM-CNN\n    YongJian Bao, Hao Yang, Zhongliang Yang, Sheng Liu\n    https://arxiv.org/pdf/1912.12871v2\n3. 1810.08136v1 | 2018-10-18 | TS-CNN: Text Steganalysis from Semantic Space Based on Convolutional Neural Network\n    Zhongliang Yang, Nan Wei, Junyi Sheng, Yongfeng Huang\n    https://arxiv.org/pdf/1810.08136v1\n4. 2406.18565v1 | 2024-06-01 | Pseudo-label Based Domain Adaptation for Zero-Shot Text Steganalysis\n    Yufei Luo, Zhen Yang, Ru Zhang, Jianyi Liu\n    https://arxiv.org/pdf/2406.18565v1\n5. 1110.3466v1 | 2011-10-16 | Effective Steganography Detection Based On Data Compression\n    Ivan Nechta\n    https://arxiv.org/pdf/1110.3466v1\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
